    <item>
      <title>巴克莱的丹尼尔·汉纳谈可持续金融</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-25/barclay-s-daniel-hanna-on-sustainable-finance-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴克莱银行全球可持续金融主管 Daniel Hanna 在伦敦举行的 2024 年彭博可持续商业峰会上与彭博社的 Kriti Gupta 讨论了该银行的转型金融方法、打击绿色清洗等。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-25/barclay-s-daniel-hanna-on-sustainable-finance-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 12:16:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>富国银行将标普 500 指数年终目标上调至 5,535 点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-25/s-p-500-year-end-target-raised-to-5-535-at-wells-fargo-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[富国银行 (Wells Fargo) 股票策略主管克里斯·哈维 (Chris Harvey) 解释了该公司对标准普尔 500 指数年底目标为 5,535 点的呼吁，并表示这并不取决于美联储今年降息的次数。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-25/s-p-500-year-end-target-raised-to-5-535-at-wells-fargo-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 12:12:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Trinny Woodall 表示，人工智能是我们前进的方向</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-25/ai-is-where-we-re-heading-says-trinny-woodall-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[化妆品牌 Trinny London 首席执行官、英国电视节目“What Not to Wear”的前联合主持人 Trinny Woodall 表示，她正在利用人工智能继续发展其主要在线业务。她在伦敦接受了彭博社的莉兹·伯登的采访。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-25/ai-is-where-we-re-heading-says-trinny-woodall-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 12:02:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伦敦证券交易所老板将跻身英国薪酬最高高管行列</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/london-stock-exchange-s-david-schwimmer-to-be-one-of-ftse-100-s-top-paid-ceos</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦证券交易所集团 (London Stock Exchange Group Plc) 的首席执行官将跻身富时 100 指数最高薪酬高管行列，股东投票决定将其最高薪酬提高一倍多，达到约 1,300 万英镑（合 1,620 万美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/london-stock-exchange-s-david-schwimmer-to-be-one-of-ftse-100-s-top-paid-ceos</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 11:57:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>土耳其在通胀峰值接近 70% 之前暂停加息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/turkey-pauses-rate-hikes-ahead-of-inflation-peaking-at-over-70</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其央行维持利率不变，一个月后暂停利率大幅加息，并自此实施进一步紧缩措施，令市场大吃一惊。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/turkey-pauses-rate-hikes-ahead-of-inflation-peaking-at-over-70</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 11:00:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡特彼勒对第二季度销量下滑发出警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/caterpillar-profit-beats-estimates-as-pricing-offsets-sales-dip</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卡特彼勒公司公布的第一季度业绩显示，机械销量较上年同期下滑，并警告称，预计第二季度这一趋势将持续。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/caterpillar-profit-beats-estimates-as-pricing-offsets-sales-dip</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 10:37:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香奈儿首席执行官表示价格上涨是由通货膨胀和工艺推动的</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/chanel-ceo-says-price-hikes-driven-by-inflation-craftsmanship</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香奈儿 (Chanel) 首席执行官为该奢侈品牌的定价进行了辩护，此前该品牌将其最著名的一款手袋的成本提高到超过 10,000 欧元（10,725 美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/chanel-ceo-says-price-hikes-driven-by-inflation-craftsmanship</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>必和必拓斥资 390 亿美元与英美资源集团合作创建矿业巨头</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/bhp-proposed-offer-valuing-anglo-american-at-31-1-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[必和必拓集团有限公司 (BHP Group Ltd.) 提议收购英美资源集团 (Anglo American Plc)，对这家规模较小的矿商的估值为 311 亿英镑（合 389 亿美元），这笔交易将打造全球最大的铜生产商，同时引发行业十多年来最大的重组。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/bhp-proposed-offer-valuing-anglo-american-at-31-1-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 06:48:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
